PN,37202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1784720909
OL,3,CHumanitarian worker monitored in
OL,4,CLondon hospital after potential Ebola
OL,5,Cexposure
OL,7,FA spokesperson for UKHSA continued:
OL,9,F"The individual is not currently
OL,10,Fdisplaying any symptoms and remains
OL,11,Fwell, but as a precautionary measure
OL,12,Fthey have been evacuated on a flight
OL,13,Fchartered solely for the evacuation,"
OL,14,Fthe agency said in a statement.
OL,16,F"They are now being assessed and
OL,17,Fmonitored in isolation by infectious
OL,18,Fdisease specialists at a London
OL,19,Fhospital.
OL,26,@qD@AOUuD@eO]xD@AOU
