PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1784720909
OL,3,CHumanitarian worker monitored in
OL,4,CLondon hospital after potential Ebola
OL,5,Cexposure
OL,7,FAs the disease progresses, vomiting
OL,8,Fand diarrhoea develop and it can lead
OL,9,Fto organ failure.
OL,11,FSome patients develop internal and
OL,12,Fexternal bleeding.
OL,14,FThere are no confirmed cases of Ebola
OL,15,Fin the UK and the risk to the general
OL,16,Fpublic remains low.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/5
