OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1784720909
OL,3,CHumanitarian worker monitored in
OL,4,CLondon hospital after potential Ebola
OL,5,Cexposure
OL,7,FRichard Pebody, Director of Epidemic
OL,8,Fand Emerging Infections at the UKHSA,
OL,9,Fsaid: "This individual has been
OL,10,Ftransferred out of an abundance of
OL,11,Fcaution, and we're pleased they remain
OL,12,Fwell."
